                <li>Accessibility auditing is unique in the category</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>More expensive than Screaming Frog ($35/mo vs $259/yr)</li>
                <li>Smaller crawl limits on lower plans</li>
                <li>Less customizable than Screaming Frog for power users</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Technical SEOs who want Screaming Frog depth in a cloud, shareable format.</div>
            <a href="https://sitebulb.com" class="tool-cta-btn" rel="nofollow">Visit site →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">05</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Lumar (DeepCrawl)</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best enterprise crawler</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">Custom<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);"></span></div>
